                                    target="#ref_Altheim. Aus Spātantike und Christentum. 1951 "
                                /></bibl>),</note>
                        <biblScope>pp. 164—165</biblScope></bibl>.— <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Gershevitch"/>
                        <biblScope>§§ 236, 391</biblScope></bibl>.—<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Benveniste._Etudes."/>
